Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
getPGPinUseSignalRoute(25.10)                    getPGPinUseSignalRoute(25.10)

Name
       getPGPinUseSignalRoute  -  Returns  all  the existing MSV settings that
       were set by the setPGPinUseSignalRoute command in the current database

Syntax
       getPGPinUseSignalRoute

       [-help]

       Returns all the existing MSV settings that were set by the  setPGPinUs-
       eSignalRoute command in the current database. Use this command to iden-
       tify the cell PG pins, which are routed by the signal router.

Parameters
       -help  Prints  out the command usage. For a detailed description of the
              command and all its parameters, use the man command:

              man getPGPinUseSignalRoute

Related Information
              * setPGPinUseSignalRoute

              * routePGPinUseSignalRoute

              * Low Power Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

